parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Tire failure and blowouts can lead to accidents, loss of control, and damage to the vehicle, which can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Tire blowouts
sidewall failures
tread separation
and loss of tire pressure
often occurring at high speeds or while driving uphill.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel System Failure due to Water Contamination
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water contamination in the fuel system can cause the engine to stall, leading to a loss of power steering and brakes, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls unexpectedly while driving
losing all power steering and brakes
the engine stops running while in motion
the fuel filter becomes clogged due to water contamination.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel filter can cause the engine to stall, leading to a loss of power steering and brakes, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls unexpectedly while driving
losing all power steering and brakes
the engine stops running while in motion
the fuel filter becomes clogged due to water contamination.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel transfer (lift) pump can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to engine stalling, loss of power steering and brakes, and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Fuel leaks
engine stalling
loss of power steering and brakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the electrical system can cause a fire, which can lead to serious damage to the vehicle and potentially harm the occupants.
symptoms: The shut-off switch for the electrical system malfunctions
wiring melts
and a fire occurs without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Chassis Connector Water Ingress and Electrical Short
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water ingress into the chassis connector can cause electrical shorts, leading to uncontrolled acceleration, loss of braking, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Error code lights illuminate
engine RPM increases on its own
brakes become hot and smoking
and transmission shifting issues occur.
